hange.</div>
<br />I once thought about using it too, but I ended up giving up on a few things, and settled for the MMC3. The background will not be as detailed as I'd like, and the sprites will not have as much animation, but it's still all good. The MMC5 is much more than a mapper, it is able to modify the console in so many ways, like in an attempt to make it less outdated.</div>

